ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 6th day of June, 2011, appellant’s Petition for Permission to Appeal from an Interlocutory Order is DISMISSED AS MOOT. See Commonwealth v. Edmiston, 613 CAP, order entered June 6, 2011.
